 (387172005), <a href="/web/20180712201020/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0023413&amp;fLockTerm=Folinic+acid">Folinic acid</a>
 (1528001), <a href="/web/20180712201020/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0023413&amp;fLockTerm=Folinic+acid">Folinic acid</a>
 (396065004), <a href="/web/20180712201020/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C1512814&amp;fLockTerm=Intensity+modulated+radiation+therapy">Intensity modulated radiation therapy</a>
 (441799006), <a href="/web/20180712201020/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0024623&amp;fLockTerm=Malignant+tumor+of+stomach">Malignant tumor of stomach</a>
